Package: BayesianHybridDesign
Title: Bayesian Hybrid Design and Analysis
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    c(
      person("Philip", "He", email =  "phe@dsi.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
      person("Zhaohua", "Lu", email = "zhaohua.lu@gmail.com", role = c("aut"))
    )
Description: This package performs the Bayesian hybrid design and analysis using dynamic power prior method. The design is applicable for primary endpoint of ORR with a historical control of the same patient population as the current trial. The historical control and the study control are incorported together to create the hybrid control.
